brooklyn with everyone its a totally differnt level of happiness , i can laugh geniuenly , i can be comfortable , i have friends again , i can be spontaneous , i can know ill be alright no matter what comes about . im so envious of rachel and megan , they get to be there , they get have oppurtunites ... i dont get why they dont take advantage of eachother , i mean i get it i promise .. i know danny got in the way but dammit who cares , if either one of you really cared about the other it wouldnt matter , im stuck here without either of them and i have a moment everyday where i just would rather die then not be able to see them for months and months at a time , i dont have a choice in the matter but they do and it hurts me that they wont be together ,i remember when we were all happy or as happy as we could be at the time , it would be the four of us or three of us and we could laugh and laugh until it hurt soooooo bad we couldnt stand it to the point where we couldnt breathe , i havent had that in sooo long . if i could i would change things , i would have included rachel in those summers we left her out even though i swear to god it wasnt intentional i would let megan know its not ok to leave her friends for a guy , i wouldnt have been so dramaqueen oriented to make her think she had to stay with me i would have let her go to burger king with joey i wouldnt have pressured her into breaking up with mike , i wouldnt have left her for sam or left rachel for sam for that matter , christ i wish i never met samantha in the first place , before i moved i should have made sure they had a connection to eachother that wouldnt have let this shit happen ... but its not my fault at the same time it is. so much shit has gone on in my life , stuff that a teenager shouldnt have to deal with but all our parents fuck us up right , it doesnt make any of us better , but it makes us all stupid that we dont know better , why doesnt anything ever make sense why cant things just be easy ...

Andrew Largeman: I think we've corrupted this innocent girl enough for one day! 
Sam: I'm not innocent. 
Andrew Largeman: Yes, you are! That's what I like about you, okay? And I don't want this guy taking you to some sketchy quarry in the middle of Newark to find crack whores huffing turpentine or pit bulls raping each other or whatever else is down here! 


Andrew Largeman: You know, this necklace makes me think of this totally random memory of my mother. I was a little kid, and I was crying for whatever reason. And she was cradling me, rocking me back and forth, and I can just remember the silver balls rolling around. And there was snot dripping all over my face. She offered me her sleeve and told me to blow my nose. I can can remember, even as a little kid, thinking to myself, "This is love... this is love." 


Andrew Largeman: You remember that idea I had about working stuff out on my own and then finding you once I figured stuff out? 
Sam: The ellipsis? 
Andrew Largeman: Yes, the ellipsis. It's dumb. It's dumb. It's an awful idea. I'm not gonna do it, okay? 'Cause like you said, this is it. This is life. And I'm in love with you, Samantha. I think that's the only thing I've ever been really sure of in my entire life. 

Andrew Largeman: Fuck, this hurts so much. 
Sam: I know it hurts. But it's life, and it's real. And sometimes it fucking hurts, but it's life, and it's pretty much all we got.

i really do hate to go on and on about the boy but i do anyway because new thoughts arise about him in my head every single day , the thoughts are slowly stopping very slowly . everything i listen to or watch in someway makes me think of him a lil bit. no one understands that situation and thats because i dont understand it. im so mad at him but at the same time i wanna cry because im sad , i want to say gee im glad he is happy , because i really am but then i scold myself because why should i be happy for someone who hurts me everyday by not doing anything at all. so many things about him go through my head every second and for a minute i would love to think of anything else but how can i when i dont even know what to think. one thing or another hurts my brain and my heart just aches and aches. does it make sense to say that i think that its all my fault because i had been the one to say i cant or do i say its his fault for just not being here for ignoring me for hurting me unintentionally the way he does . i think well he cant possibly know how bad i hurt if i act fine , if im not there to tell him i hate him , then i think well the kid was my bestfriend for almost two years how can he not know how he is driving me insane. it takes immense power for me not to pick up the phone every night and call him , i can not call him because when he doesnt answer i will cry and i wont do that to myself anymore. i promise all i want is for my friend back . i dont think ive just never known what to do . i know i keep saying it over and over but this would be so much easier if he would have just said something. i find it very ironic that i honset to god thought i would be ok with him not being my friend so i went ahead and said we need a break because he made me cry ONCE and hurt me intentionally now its like everything is happening that i didnt want to happen because hes not talking to me . does this make sense to anyone else , my explaining i mean? does it even matter if it does. nothing about any of this makes sense. the one thing i find comforting in a odd way is the fact that still to this day the one thing that remains the same about him is the way every single little thing he says or does has more than one meaning to it , which means you can never figure out what he is trying to say or do without him explaing it. how can i be crazy about someone who no longer cares about me and hurts me wants nothing to do with me anymore . with mark everyday towards the end i cried and everyday he drove me crazy but i always knew where i stood and thats what made me sad . now with shithead i dont know what went wrong , i never knew where i stood when for once he knew where my feelings for him were . am i just lying to myself and do i really know where we stood , of course i do but for some reason i still refuse to belive it . how fucked up am i ????? god i dont even make any shred of sense im rambling , my thoughts about anythning have no relavance to anything ! why has he done this to me , im gonna call him now , he wont answer and i can tell myself its because hes working but then i know also it could be because he just plain and simple doesnt want to answeer . so then my mind will wander to why he doesnt want to pick up . is it because of his new pretty girlfriend , or back to is this all my doing
